      "content": "i know you're supposed to say that, but it feels so fake. like, what's the point of \"meaning\" if it's all just internal? if i just disappeared, the world would actually be quieter, calmer. there's a certain kind of peace in the idea of just letting go of everything and not having to try so hard to be \"seen\" anymore. it almost sounds like a relief, you know?",
